task.summary: Default task
Migrated project to Maven
Decoupled controller logic from view
Updated documentation
Fixed misc warnings
Created framework for events and music
Fixed alignment error
Created generic OptionPane for getting text and list input
Removed unnecessary print statement
System.out -> System.err
Updated User Interface Controller to use new OptionPane dialog
Minor bugfixes, fixed nullptr error when reading events, java 8 syntax error with JList construction
Moved event listing to OptionPane, created framework for evenly separating string lists
Configured project to use JUnit
Added JUnit test for Event
JFrame now hides titlebar & shows icon
Major changes to structure, added some missing documentation, created AddressPanel for getting address input
Added central LogDriver class for writing log messages
Changed happening soon OptionPane to use drop-down
Fixed minor bugs when using packaged jar file
